Popular Nigerian singer, Simisola Bolatito Ogunleye, better known by her stage name Simi, has predicted who she thinks will win this year’s season of the Big Brother Naija show. The “Joromi” crooner, who performed at the last BBNaija Sunday Live Show, was asked to say who she thinks will take home the 45 million naira prize money during a quiz segment titled “Quiz Me” powered by DStv. The singing sensation picked Miracle who seems to be in the good books of many Nigerians as he is getting a lot of love and support from them right now. Watch video below:  Aside Simi, Popular OAP Daddy Freeze and DJ Exclusive, who recently performed at one of the weekly house parties, have also predicted that the 23-year-old pilot will win the show. The post Simi Predicts Who Will Win This Year’s #BBNaija (Watch Video) appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.